<th style="border: none; background: transparent;"><span id="WP:ALIVE"></span><span id="WP:BLP"></span><span id="WP:LIVE"></span><small><a href="Wikipedia_Shortcut" title="Wikipedia:Shortcut">Shortcuts</a>:<br />
<a href="Wikipedia_ALIVE" title="Wikipedia:ALIVE" class="mw-redirect">WP:ALIVE</a><br />
<a href="index.html" title="Wikipedia:BLP" class="mw-redirect">WP:BLP</a><br />
