<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-32"><a href="#Summary_deletion.2C_creation_prevention.2C_and_courtesy_blanking"><span class="tocnumber">6.1</span> <span class="toctext">Summary deletion, creation prevention, and courtesy blanking</span></a></li>
